Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:18.56,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要喚出情感之名 則無休無止無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:26.65,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神傳來呼喚 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:28.49,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:29.74,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不離不棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:33.33,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無論光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:37.21,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如緊湊相連的拼圖零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.46,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:45.71,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罷
