Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:23:00.98,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無虛情假意 非利益所趨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:05.73,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真實自我
